{"tid":1966030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：本港要應對「經濟戰疫」","createTime":"2020-04-10T01:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T01:32:49.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07887aa74a2d96d3ee87d158603735727d942fa0","tid":1966030,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"邱騰華：本港要應對「經濟戰疫」<br />\n10.04.2020 08:34<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華，在一個電台節目表示，本港除了要應對新型冠狀病毒疫情，亦要應對「經濟戰疫」，受疫情影響，部分中小企的生意少了八成，個別甚至差不多完全停頓。他表示，政府為了協助中小微企資金周轉，決定改良三個借貸擔保計劃，其中「百分百擔保特惠貸款」，上限由現時的200萬元，增加至400萬元，企業只須還息、毋須還本，相信有3萬多間中小微企合資格申請，最快今個月20日推出，現時已有部分銀行有興趣參與，亦已經開始準備前期工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279916&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279916%26csid%3D261_341&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi695k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=c6997388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279916&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ed35d424981fc48fec3997fdde71ef16fa436ffb","tid":1966030,"uid":186071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:25:50.000Z","msg":"上年差過沙士 咁依家係咩？"},{"pid":"78e26eca3275b2427b42d05b66c2bad0e983662a","tid":1966030,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed35d424981fc48fec3997fdde71ef16fa436ffb","tid":1966030,"uid":186071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:25:50.000Z","msg":"上年差過沙士 咁依家係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"衰過佔中！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c630ee7d549000fc3eb7ab5a04b280373c5faba","tid":1966030,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78e26eca3275b2427b42d05b66c2bad0e983662a","tid":1966030,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed35d424981fc48fec3997fdde71ef16fa436ffb","tid":1966030,"uid":186071,"like":3,"disl